# Template Lint Checklist

Use this checklist whenever applying templates to a new project.

## Placeholder Integrity
- [ ] No unresolved placeholders remain (e.g., `[PROJECT_NAME]`, `[VERIFY_COMMAND]`)
- [ ] Commands are executable on target OS/runtime
- [ ] File links point to existing files

## Governance Integrity
- [ ] `AI_AGENT.md` exists at project root
- [ ] `docs/constitution/AI_SOURCE_OF_TRUTH.md` exists and references startup order
- [ ] `docs/INSTRUCTIONS_INDEX.md` includes all core workflow docs
- [ ] `CHANGELOG.md` exists and has `Unreleased` section
- [ ] `docs/GAME_PLAN.md` exists with phase statuses
- [ ] `docs/PROJECT_TIER_POLICY.md` exists and selected tier is recorded

## Quality Gate Integrity
- [ ] Verify command is defined and works
- [ ] Smoke command exists and runs
- [ ] At least one targeted workflow test exists
- [ ] Workflow matrix maps each key workflow to a command

## Operations Integrity
- [ ] Manual smoke runbook exists and is executable
- [ ] Deployment runbook exists with rollback section
- [ ] Secrets policy exists and matches runtime environment

## Tier-Control Integrity
- [ ] Tier A: advanced docs may be `N/A` with rationale
- [ ] Tier B: ADR/Risk/Release/Security/Observability docs are present or `N/A` with rationale
- [ ] Tier C: ADR/Risk/Release/Security/Observability docs are present and executable

## AI Context Integrity
- [ ] AI context generator exists and runs
- [ ] `AI_CONTEXT.md` generated successfully
- [ ] AI startup order is consistent across docs
